== Reactivate Staff Member ==
Operator -> System : Reactivate Staff Member (staffId)
alt Staff member not found
  System --> Operator : Error: Staff member not found
else Already active
  System --> Operator : Error: Staff member already active
else Success
  System --> Operator : Staff member reactivated\n(ActivityStatus = ACTIVE)
end

